        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[13px] font-medium text-zinc-900 group-hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors">How to Create Bug Reports with Screenshots</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider">QA and developer workflows</p>
        </div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-300 ml-auto group-hover:text-sky-500 transition-colors">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/how-to/how-to-make-onboarding-guides-for-saas/" class="product-card group p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
        <img src="/ext-icons/procshot.png" alt="Procshot" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg" />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[13px] font-medium text-zinc-900 group-hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors">How to Make Onboarding Guides for SaaS</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Customer success and PM workflows</p>
        </div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-300 ml-auto group-hover:text-sky-500 transition-colors">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/how-to/how-to-export-tutorials-to-pdf-markdown/" class="product-card group p-4 flex items-center gap-3">
        <img src="/ext-icons/procshot.png" alt="Procshot" class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg" />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-[13px] font-medium text-zinc-900 group-hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors">How to Export Tutorials to PDF or Markdown</h3>
          <p class="font-mono text-[9px] text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Format guide for technical writers</p>
        </div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-300 ml-auto group-hover:text-sky-500 transition-colors">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-zinc-100">
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">// compare procshot</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="/compare/procshot-vs-scribe/" class="text-[12px] text-zinc-600 hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors font-mono">Procshot vs Scribe →</a>
        <a href="/compare/procshot-vs-tango/" class="text-[12px] text-zinc-600 hover:text-sky-600 transition-colors font-mono">Procshot vs Tango →</a>
